206
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:07,400
tak si ji drž na řetězu.

207
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:09,530
Drž hubu!

208
00:13:11,430 --> 00:13:12,400
Okawo!

209
00:13:14,330 --> 00:13:16,220
